Use Case 01

CHARACTERISTIC INFORMATION
Goal in Context
As a statistician, I want to be able to see a report of
                                                        All the countries in the world organised by largest population to smallest.
                                                        OR
                                                        All the countries in a continent organised by largest population to smallest.
                                                        OR
                                                        All the countries in a region organised by largest population to smallest
Scope
Company.
Level
Primary task.
Preconditions
We know the role. Database contains current country, city and population data .
Success End Condition
A report is available for statistician.
Failed End Condition
No report is produced.
Primary Actor
Statistician .
Trigger
A request for population information is sent to statistician.
MAIN SUCCESS SCENARIO
Population information is requested.
Statistician extracts report of
                                All the countries in the world organised by largest population to smallest.
                                OR
                                All the countries in a continent organised by largest population to smallest.
                                OR
                                All the countries in a region organised by largest population to smallest
Statistician provides report.
EXTENSIONS

SUB-VARIATIONS
None.
SCHEDULE
DUE DATE: Release 2.0